"Kediaman Tatsuo"

213
00:11:38.987 --> 00:11:40.787
Yoshiro.

214
00:11:40.787 --> 00:11:42.387
Koji.

215
00:11:42.387 --> 00:11:45.387
Ayaka. Shigetsugu.

216
00:11:45.387 --> 00:11:48.987
